OL,3,CBank of England must better address
OL,4,Cclimate risk to tackle inflation, WWF
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Bank of England must better
OL,8,Faddress environmental risks to manage
OL,9,Finflation and ensure the UK's long-
OL,10,Fterm financial stability, campaigners
OL,11,Fhave said.
OL,13,FThe central bank is being urged to
OL,14,Ftake a series of actions, including
OL,15,Fdeveloping more technical expertise on
OL,16,Fclimate and nature-related risks to
OL,17,Fthe economy, in a paper by wildlife
OL,18,Fcharity WWF.
