OL,3,CBank of England must better address
OL,4,Cclimate risk to tackle inflation, WWF
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe report, released on Monday,
OL,8,Foutlines the negative impacts of
OL,9,Fclimate change and nature loss on
OL,10,Fprice stability, financial stability
OL,11,Fand growth, which it points to as the
OL,12,Fbedrocks of the UK economy and
OL,13,Fpeople's living standards.
OL,15,FIt argues that the Bank of England is
OL,16,Ffalling behind other central banks in
OL,17,Fmanaging environmental threats and can
OL,18,Fbetter align with and support the
OL,19,Ftransition to a net zero, nature-
OL,20,Fpositive economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
