OL,3,CBank of England must better address
OL,4,Cclimate risk to tackle inflation, WWF
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FKaren Ellis, WWF's chief economist,
OL,8,Fsaid: "There is so much more they
OL,9,Fcould and should be doing.
OL,11,F"The financial sector has a huge
OL,12,Fimpact on climate change, which is
OL,13,Fleading to growing economic pressures
OL,14,Fin the UK, like food price rises and
OL,15,Fmaking properties uninsurable due to
OL,16,Fincreasing flood risk.
