OL,3,CBank of England must better address
OL,4,Cclimate risk to tackle inflation, WWF
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"As one of the most powerful bodies
OL,8,Ftasked with regulating this sector,
OL,9,Fthe Bank of England's actions matter
OL,10,Ffor climate and nature, and frankly
OL,11,Fthe Bank of England and their well-
OL,12,Fresourced team must do more."
OL,14,FWWF is calling on the Bank to improve
OL,15,Fits analysis of the impacts of climate
OL,16,Fchange and nature loss on the economy,
OL,17,Fand communicate these findings widely
OL,18,Fto policymakers, politicians and the
OL,19,Fpublic.
