OL,3,CBank of England must better address
OL,4,Cclimate risk to tackle inflation, WWF
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe charity said it should also align
OL,8,Fits own policymaking with an orderly
OL,9,Ftransition ` drawing on examples of
OL,10,Fbest practice from other central banks
OL,11,Faround the world, while also
OL,12,Fdeveloping its own innovative
OL,13,Fproposals.
OL,15,FOther recommendations include adapting
OL,16,Fits market operations to better align
OL,17,Fwith an orderly transition and co-
OL,18,Fordinating with government fiscal
OL,19,Fpolicy and industrial strategy to
OL,20,Fensure it can more effectively respond
OL,21,Fto climate-induced supply side shocks.
