OL,3,CBank of England must better address
OL,4,Cclimate risk to tackle inflation, WWF
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt is not the first time campaigners
OL,8,Fhave urged the Bank to step up action
OL,9,Fon environmental risks.
OL,11,FIn March last year, more than 50
OL,12,Fleading economists and campaign groups
OL,13,Fwrote a letter to governor Andrew
OL,14,FBailey, warning him that the Bank is
OL,15,Fslipping behind other major central
OL,16,Fbanks.
