OL,3,CBank of England must better address
OL,4,Cclimate risk to tackle inflation, WWF
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt came after the Bank reduced
OL,8,Fresources towards climate change work,
OL,9,Fwhich Mr Bailey said was made after
OL,10,Fthe Treasury changed its list of
OL,11,Fpriorities for the financial services
OL,12,Fsector.
OL,14,FClimate change is increasingly
OL,15,Fdisrupting food supplies, which in
OL,16,Fturn is driving up price inflation and
OL,17,Fthe overall cost of living.
